"From 'I' to 'We' — our forever begins.
In the blink of a moment, two souls became one. Not just in the eyes of the world, but in every heartbeat, every breath, every dream.
We stood hand in hand, promising to walk through chaos and calm, laughter and tears — always together.
This isn’t just a wedding. It’s a story of love, faith, destiny — and everything in between.
Today, we don’t just celebrate a ceremony. We celebrate a lifetime that begins with a vow, sealed with love, and filled with memories waiting to be made.
Here’s to every sunset we’ll watch together, every challenge we’ll conquer, and every dream we’ll chase side by side. 💍✨
#JustMarried #ForeverAndAlways"
